OL,3,CHow much should Guernsey's minimum
OL,4,Cwage increase by?
OL,6,FGuernsey's politicians return from
OL,7,Ftheir summer break today (4th
OL,8,FSeptember) and among the topics up for
OL,9,Fdebate is the island's minimum wage
OL,10,Fand by how much it should increase.
OL,12,FThe initial plan was to raise it for
OL,13,Fadults from #10.65 an hour to #12.
OL,15,FHowever, some politicians argue this
OL,16,Fis too high and believe it would put
OL,17,Ftoo much pressure on employers and
OL,18,Fcould ultimately lead to higher prices
OL,19,Ffor consumers.
