OL,3,CHow much should Guernsey's minimum
OL,4,Cwage increase by?
OL,6,FAs a result, Deputies Inder and
OL,7,FVermeulen have submitted an amendment
OL,8,Fadvocating for a smaller rise in the
OL,9,Fminimum wage to either #11.25 or
OL,10,F#11.55, depending on the opinions of
OL,11,Fother politicians.
OL,13,FAny changes will take effect from 1st
OL,14,FOctober this year.
